<p>Using the open-source ChatGPT Web project as a container, I&rsquo;ve set up a domain-accessible <strong>ChatGPT UI</strong>. Chain: <code>(Domain -&gt; DNS -&gt; Nginx -&gt;) Cloud Function Proxy -&gt; OpenAI</code></p>
